    "body": "int main() {\n  ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);\n  cin.tie(nullptr);\n  int ${1:t} = 1;\n  cin >> $1;\n  while ($1--) {\n    solve();\n  }\n  return 0;\n}",
    "description": "Full main() skeleton with test cases"
  },
